          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the dough",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Whisk together the {{plain-flour}}, {{baking-powder}}, {{mixed-spice}}, and {{sea-salt-fine}}. Rub in the cold {{unsalted-butter}} with your fingertips until the mixture resembles breadcrumbs. Stir in the {{caster-sugar}} and {{dried-currants}}. Add the beaten {{eggs}} and mix until the dough just comes together, add a splash of {{whole-milk}} only if needed. It should be firm enough to roll.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Roll and cook, 2 to 3 minutes per side",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Roll the dough on a lightly floured surface to about 8 mm thick. Cut into rounds with a 6 cm cutter. Heat a heavy frying pan or griddle over medium-low heat until hot. This is ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "griddle cooking",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp9yj1bd000058v49k5gwpff"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": ": no fat in the pan. Cook the cakes for 2 to 3 minutes on the first side until the underside is evenly coloured, then flip and cook for 2 to 3 minutes on the second side. The cakes should feel firm when pressed. Dust with caster sugar immediately.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
